# /add-screen — Scaffold React Native Screen

Follow Navigation v1.4.5 patterns (29 existing screens).

## Checklist
1. **Register** in Screen Registry (sec 1) — sequential ID, app, version tag
2. **Navigation Flow** — assign to parent flow (sec 3)
3. **Tab Bar** — if top-level, add to tab config + badge logic
4. **Deep link** — register `robinfood://` route (sec 4), auth-gate redirect
5. **Push routing** — add to Push → Screen table (sec 9)
6. **Offline** — Buyer: blocking overlay; Picker: local queue
7. **Error/Empty states** — add to sec 8 table
8. **A11y** — WCAG AA: 44×44pt targets, 4.5:1 contrast, accessibilityLabel, formatPrice()
9. **Transitions** — follow sec 7 animation table (fade 150ms, slide 300ms, modal 250ms)
10. **Localization** — all strings in resource files, no hardcoded text

